-article/.premium/israels-defense-chief-dont-let-pyromaniac-ben-gvir-be-part-of-new-war-cabinet/00000190-e477-d566-adfa-ef77edad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人面临新的恐惧：无人机袭击期间住在高楼里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-fear-unlocked-for-israelis-living-in-high-rises-during-drone-attacks/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</link><description>当一架无人机击中以色列高层建筑时，楼上居民只能孤军奋战：上周胡塞武装袭击特拉维夫，这对一个摩天大楼之国来说是个坏兆头，因为这个国家没有办法保护他们</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-fear-unlocked-for-israelis-living-in-high-rises-during-drone-attacks/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士认为内塔尼亚胡赞成达成协议，但将避免在国会演讲中这么说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡访问期间民主党的回避强化了他和特朗普的说法，因为他们寻求重建关系。尽管所有人的目光都集中在总理的讲话上，但很少有人注意到司法政变的卷土重来</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</guid></item><item><title>一场失败的比赛：加沙战争导致海外球员远离以色列体育遭受干旱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</link><description>运动员不敢与以色列队签约，他们的父母拒绝让他们来，经纪人也要求更多的钱。只有那些已经在以色列打过球的人才准备好本赛季在这里打球——除了财力雄厚的三巨头篮球俱乐部</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</guid></item><item><title>新特拉维夫咖啡馆致力于治愈 10 月 7 日四分五裂的社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</link><description>特拉维夫最新的连锁咖啡店 Café Otef 的每家分店均由疏散的基布兹成员经营并配备员工，所有收益都捐献给社区。 “你需要早上醒来并忙碌起来，这就是我们的孩子们现在看到的我们正在做的事情，”负责基布兹雷伊姆分部的罗伊特说</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</guid></item><item><title>报告：Nova 节幸存者讲述哈马斯恐怖分子如何在 10 月 7 日强奸他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</link><description>以色列第 12 频道的匿名报道与去年法国报纸上发表的报道一样 ■ 详细描述 10 月 7 日强奸事件的报道以及营救幸存者和第一个到达现场的人的证词浮出水面</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将就伊朗的侵略向国会发出警告。但他的伊朗政策却是一个巨大的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</link><description>当以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中提到伊朗时，鉴于他在这个问题上长达数十年的可怕、甚至是灾难性的记录，世界应该将其视为采取完全相反行动的信号</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:50:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</guid></item>