um/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</link><description>拜登承诺将利用其总统任期的最后几个月来确保加沙停火和人质返回，但即将卸任的总统将拥有多少精力还有待观察 ■ 据与内塔尼亚胡关系密切的人士透露，内塔尼亚胡并没有放弃人质协议 — — 或者与沙特阿拉伯的正常化协议 — — 但如果他确实选择达成协议，他仍然面临严重障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，等待拜登和内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论后离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡预计将在抗议和立法者抵制之际在国会发表讲话 ■ 内塔尼亚胡游说白宫和国会向以色列运送美国扣留的重型炸弹 ■ 真主党播放无人机视频，称其显示以色列纵深的以色列国防军空军基地 ■ 国防军称拦截了两架在以色列发射的无人机来自东部 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在北部受重伤，两人在加沙战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四在白宫会见拜登，周五将在海湖庄园会见特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</link><description>白宫确认，拜登总统将在以色列总理向国会发表讲话以及拜登向全国发表黄金时段讲话后不到 24 小时会见内塔尼亚胡，他将在讲话中首次阐述他不竞选连任的决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</guid></item><item><title>议会为人力资源机构雇员提供免遭性骚扰的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</link><description>该修正案还将禁止歧视性骚扰投诉者的规定扩大到通过此类机构雇用的工人</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列总检察长拒绝上诉，2021 年骚乱中阿拉伯人被犹太人杀害的案件仍将结案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</link><description>穆萨·哈苏纳的家人声称，此案的调查存在缺陷，是迫于政治压力而结束的。总检察长驳回上诉的决定并未解决这些主张</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:42:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在哈里斯-夏皮罗选票中看到希望，同时准备迎接反犹太主义风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</link><description>在庆祝卡玛拉·哈里斯成为民主党推定提名人的同时，美国犹太人应该做好准备，迎接唐纳德·特朗普的基地将面临的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</guid></item><item><title>教育部长表示，以色列与黎巴嫩边境附近的学校不会在秋季重新开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</link><description>教育部长约夫·基什在解释他九月份不重新开放北部社区学校的决定时告诉北部市长，“我们别无选择，只能决定对黎巴嫩发动一场激烈的战争”。自战争爆发以来，超过 16,000 名学生从北方撤离</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:10:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 291 天：内塔尼亚胡表示人质返回的条件“正在成熟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</link><description>世界卫生组织警告，由于健康和卫生条件不佳，加沙及其他地区小儿麻痹症爆发的风险很高。定居者 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫称他们签署了宣言，誓言组建联合政府 ■ 战争开始 291 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</guid></item></channel></rss>